Wait, don't go in yet.

7
00:00:18,519 --> 00:00:19,000
Wait.

8
00:00:26,480 --> 00:00:27,160
Mom

9
00:00:32,560 --> 00:00:34,840
Happy birthday!

10
00:00:35,399 --> 00:00:36,960
Thank you, kids.

11
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:37,960
Dong

12
